23
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:46,720
Yes.

24
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:47,920
Look at Ye Qiming.

25
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,520
No matter what,

26
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,210
he's from the countryside.

27
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:52,479
Mom,

28
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:54,840
Qiming is capable and ambitious.

29
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,050
I believe in him.

30
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:56,560
No,

31
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,240
girl, listen to your dad.

32
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,700
He's from the countryside

33
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,980
and has no background.

34
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:03,240
What kind of future will he have?

35
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,340
If you are with him,

36
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:06,880
you'll have nothing to eat.

37
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:08,560
What's wrong with being from the countryside?

38
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,880
Ye Qiming studies very hard at school.

39
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,730
I believe he'll be successful.

40
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,460
About this matter,

41
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:16,760
your mom and I have already decided.

42
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,079
It's settled.

43
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,920
Whoever wants to go can go.

44
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:22,120
I'm not going anyway.

45
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:23,360
Linlin!

46
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,160
This kid...

47
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,560
Mom, Dad.

48
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,820
Linlin is back.

49
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,360
Our daughter is back.

50
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,240
Here, give it to me.

51
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,480
It's fine. I've got it.

52
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:44,320
Listen, sweetheart.

53
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:45,920
You've finally figured it out.

54
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:46,400
Good.

55
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,320
Hurry up and leave that brat.

56
