61
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,480
Wait, what do you still need to calm down about?

62
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,880
Just leave him.

63
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,920
Dad, what are you talking about?

64
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,960
