67
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,520
What do you mean what they'll think?

68
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,680
There are plenty of good guys out there.

69
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:13,080
Hurry up and divorce him.

70
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,000
How can a father

71
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,320
tell his child to get a divorce?

72
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:17,400
