81
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:32,320
Why can't you still accept his father?

82
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:33,160
Let me tell you.

83
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,960
He doesn't respect me as his father-in-law at all.

84
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,120
Qiming,

85
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,480
I asked you out today

86
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:53,160
to talk to you about something.

87
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,079
Go ahead, Dad.

88
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,370
That plot of land

89
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,720
is very important to my company.

90
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:05,040
Can you let us have it?

91
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:05,960
Dad,

92
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:07,120
I understand.

93
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:10,040
But I have to be responsible for my company.

94
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,920
Let's just compete fairly.

95
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,280
Dad,

96
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,480
As my elder,

97
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,880
I should listen to you.

98
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,880
But the company has a board of directors,

99
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,800
and everyone is watching this project.

100
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,659
I really can't justify it to them.

101
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:35,840
I hope you can understand.

102
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,700
You are my son-in-law.

103
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,250
Can't we be on the same page?

104
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,040
Dad,

105
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,320
You didn't win the bid.

106
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,800
That's because you underestimated the market.

107
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,130
You can't blame others.

108
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:48,880
Anyway,

109
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,720
he doesn't care about me at all.

110
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,380
I have to get involved in this.

111
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:55,400
You really shouldn't interfere.

112
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,920
How am I interfering?

113
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:58,240
My daughter is the apple of my eye.

114
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,360
She's my sweet girl.

115
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,040
I have to care.

116
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:00,480
Okay.

117
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,760
Stop arguing, you two.

118
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:02,840
I'll just leave, okay?

119
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,600
Look at you, really.

120
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:05,440
Linlin.

121
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:07,760
I'm doing this for your own good.

122
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,320
You kid.

123
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,200
Go wherever you want.

124
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,440
Just don't come back!

125
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,240
No.

126
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:30,640
Stop it.

127
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,530
Give it to me.

128
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,200
No.

129
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,100
You're so naughty.

130
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,040
Xia Lin.

131
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:58,159
Auntie.

132
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:00,680
What happened to Xia Lin?

133
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:03,320
Her father forced her to marry that guy Liu.

134
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,280
She refused to do so.

135
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,480
Finally she drank a lot of medicine.

136
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,810
And now she's like this.

137
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,000
Auntie.

138
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,640
Is Xia Lin in danger of dying?

139
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,880
The doctor pumped her stomach.

140
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,560
She's out of danger now.

141
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:19,040
Got it.

142
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:23,900
You still have the nerve to come here.

143
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,530
It's all because of you.

144
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:26,420
Get out.

145
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:28,400
Get out.

146
00:06:29,080 --> 00:06:29,600
Get out.

147
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,020
Get out.

148
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:32,530
It's all because of you.

149
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:33,760
Get out.

150
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:34,840
Get out.

151
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,000
Linlin is awake.

152
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,120
Linlin. Miss.

153
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:37,580
Linlin.

154
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:38,400
Miss.

155
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,280
Linlin.

156
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,280
Just let us be together.

157
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,280
Okay?

158
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:47,650
What did you say?

159
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,560
I said,

160
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,840
I want to marry Qiming.

161
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:54,960
I beg you.

162
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:00,240
I beg you.

163
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,800
Okay.

164
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,240
Dad promises you.

165
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:06,940
Your business,

166
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,680
your mom and I won't interfere anymore.

167
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,840
But don't do this stupid thing.

168
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,460
It's not worth it for this boy.

169
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,160
I know.

170
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:19,080
Don't scare Mom and Dad again.

171
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:21,320
I'm sorry.

172
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:35,760
Hello.

173
00:07:36,159 --> 00:07:38,080
We are from the Tongjiang Police Department.

174
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:40,640
Your son, Lu Yang, has suffered gas poisoning.

175
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:41,640
Please come here.

176
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,000
Officer.

177
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,760
Did you make a mistake?

178
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:46,800
Did you make a mistake?

179
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:49,080
My Yangyang is such a good kid.

180
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,280
How could this happen?

181
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:52,280
Calm down.

182
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:58,640
What exactly

183
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,660
happened to our Yangyang?

184
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,240
He's still so young.

185
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:08,460
We are still investigating further.

186
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,200
Lu Yang's mother,

187
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:13,080
