189
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:21,640
He usually only comes home for the New Year.

190
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:24,900
We rarely contact each other either.

191
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:28,560
But he recently sent some money home.

192
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:31,300
Did he say where this money came from?

193
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,600
He said he earned it from tutoring.

194
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:37,720
This child,

195
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,580
