196
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,460
He's been very sensible since he was little.

197
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:46,640
If I had known, I would have asked him more.

198
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:51,560
Lu Yang's mom,

199
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:52,890
