201
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,560
I can't accept this. I don't want money.

202
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:57,800
I want to know...

203
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,800
I want to know the truth.

204
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,320
I beg you.

205
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,160
Lu Yang's mother.

206
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:03,920
I want to know the truth.

207
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,920
My... my son.

208
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,880
My son is still so young.

209
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:10,160
I want to know the truth.

210
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:14,200
I beg you.

211
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:16,520
I want to know the truth.

212
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:17,040
Okay, okay, okay.

213
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:20,720
I want to know the truth.

214
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,620
Come, Mr. Zhao.

215
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,770
Open your mouth.

216
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,280
Don't bite me.

217
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,380
Captain Jiang.

218
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,280
Cheer up.

219
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:42,040
This Lu Yang thing is indeed a bit...

220
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,200
But in our line of work,

221
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:46,330
isn't this kind of thing quite normal?

222
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:49,720
A campus loan and a honey trap.

223
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,680
Lu Yang is so unlucky.

224
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:52,720
Nowadays,

225
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:55,000
there are more and more methods of online fraud.

226
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,930
It's really hard to guard against.

227
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,680
By the way, Captain Shen.

228
00:09:58,680 --> 00:09:59,640
When you were in school,

229
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:01,240
did you ever encounter online fraud?

230
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:03,570
There was no internet when I was in school.

231
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:04,970
Sorry, let me ask again.

232
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:05,920
Li,

233
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:08,160
have you ever encountered fraud?

234
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:09,680
When I was in school,

235
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:13,240
I met a girl online.

236
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,680
The day I just met her,

237
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:17,000
Okay, stop right there.

238
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,060
Come on, everyone.

239
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,120
Take the buns,

240
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:20,000
and think about it yourselves.

241
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,040
Meeting adjourned.

242
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:21,760
Let's go.

243
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:27,620
Did Lu Yang have any unusual behavior normally?

244
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:28,680
No.

245
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:30,360
Wait, no.

246
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:32,880
I don't know where he usually

247
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,360
got so much money

248
00:10:34,640 --> 00:10:35,440
to drink foreign liquor.

249
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,160
Among you classmates,

250
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:37,620
who was closest to Lu Yang?

251
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,050
It's Huang Xiaoyun.

252
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:41,280
They are boyfriend and girlfriend now.

253
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,520
They often go shopping, chatting,

254
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:44,680
