263
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,530
for about 100 yuan each.

264
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:05,280
Then that's only 1,600 yuan a month.

265
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,250
That's about it.

266
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:10,360
But he also often treats his classmates to meals,

267
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:12,360
so almost all of this money is spent.

268
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:15,320
Right, Lu Yang has a loan.

269
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,480
For every 1,000 yuan he borrows,

270
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:19,340
