271
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,140
Where did the money come from?

272
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,600
I remember now.

273
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:26,570
I heard Tongda Company had sponsored Lu Yang.

274
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:32,920
Miss Yu.

275
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:33,680
Excuse me.

276
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:35,180
Please come in, officers.

277
00:11:36,880 --> 00:11:37,480
Excuse me.

278
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:38,520
