281
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,140
No need, let's talk business.

282
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:49,640
Okay.

283
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,920
Well, we came to your company today

284
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:53,000
