285
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,840
your company's sponsorship of college students.

286
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,680
Is it convenient for you?

287
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:56,160
It is.

288
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:57,200
Liu.

289
00:11:57,680 --> 00:12:01,080
Bring the bills over quickly for the two police officers to see.

290
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:01,560
Here.

291
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:05,940
Our Mr. Ye is a very caring entrepreneur.

292
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:08,360
He not only sponsors poor college students,

293
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:10,320
but also set up scholarships for them.

294
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:10,780
Really?

295
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:11,280
Yes.

296
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:13,690
But there's a classmate named Lu Yang.

297
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,500
Are you familiar with him?

298
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,400
Lu Yang.

299
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,200
I do have some impression of him.

300
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,200
So you do know him.

301
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,080
Here's the thing.

302
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,320
I'm the company's finance officer,

303
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:30,360
so I review all the bills one by one.

304
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:31,880
I remember it was on there.

305
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:33,940
You two can check it again carefully.

306
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:35,640
Understood.

307
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:37,920
In that case, we won't bother you any longer.

308
00:12:37,920 --> 00:12:39,240
Wait a minute, officers.

309
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:42,960
Are you still investigating Tian Liang's case?

310
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:46,610
You seem very interested in this case, Mr. Yu.

311
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,240
No, no.

312
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:50,380
I won't keep you then. Please.

313
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,400
Sorry to bother you, Manager Yu.

314
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:55,060
No problem.

315
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,240
See you next time.

316
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:56,720
Alright.

317
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,320
Thank you.

318
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:19,120
Ye Qiming is quite caring.

319
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:21,200
He even sponsors college students.

320
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:25,610
Why do you look so preoccupied?

321
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:27,920
Nothing.

322
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:30,080
I just have a bad feeling.

323
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:32,560
I feel like I'm going to get scolded.

324
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:34,320
Usually you're the one scolding others.

325
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,850
Who would dare to scold you?

326
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,090
That's true.

327
00:13:43,400 --> 00:13:44,200
Captain Shen.

328
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:46,340
Let's discuss something.

329
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:49,800
Hello, Chief.

330
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:51,360
Hello, Chief.

331
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,100
No, you heard it wrong.

332
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,280
Right, yes.

333
00:13:56,560 --> 00:13:57,240
Right away.

334
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:11,680
I'll say a few words on behalf of Captain Jiang for today's meeting.

335
00:14:11,680 --> 00:14:13,360
There's no progress on Tian Liang's case,

336
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:15,200
and now this happened with Lu Yang.

337
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:17,060
If anyone has any thoughts today,

338
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:18,080
let's discuss them together.

339
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:18,880
I'll go first.

340
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,680
I think merging Lu Yang's case

341
00:14:20,680 --> 00:14:22,760
with the severed arm case for investigation

342
00:14:22,760 --> 00:14:23,890
is very reasonable.

343
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:26,380
These are Lu Yang's recent expenses.

344
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:28,000
He spent money like water.

345
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:30,980
He was still paying off campus loans.

346
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:33,850
And last month, he sent 50,000 yuan to his family.

347
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:36,180
An expense of 100,000 yuan a month

348
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:37,320
for anyone

349
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,520
is not a small amount.

350
00:14:40,160 --> 00:14:42,290
This was Lu Yang's legitimate income.

351
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:44,400
Working as a tutor every month,

352
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:45,480
he earned 1,600 yuan.

353
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:47,560
Tongda Company sponsored him 2,000 yuan.

354
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:49,760
It all adds up to a mere 3,600 yuan.

355
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:51,970
This is a far cry from his expenses.

356
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:54,520
Where did the extra money come from?

357
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:56,980
This is the focus of our next investigation.

358
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,400
Most ways to make money quickly

359
00:14:58,400 --> 00:14:59,800
are illegal.

360
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:01,440
For instance, gambling,

361
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:03,240
stealing, robbing, extortion,

362
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:04,620
or being a kept man.

363
00:15:04,880 --> 00:15:05,520
As for gambling,

364
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:06,840
to reach this income level,

365
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:08,200
he'd need a certain amount of capital.

366
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,440
And once he got stuck,

367
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:10,780
he'd lose everything.

368
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:11,920
For Lu Yang,

369
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:14,080
the chances of stealing and robbing aren't high.

370
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:15,640
With Huang Xiaoyun around,

371
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:18,130
he doesn't seem like a kept man either.

372
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:20,610
So there is only one possibility left,

373
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:21,970
which is blackmail.

374
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:24,700
That is indeed the most likely possibility.

375
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,930
Then whose secret did Lu Yang have?

376
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:30,280
Ye Qiming.
